A '''heat induction unit''' was an internal device on at least some [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech droids]]. When activated, it could generate heat up to several thousand degrees. The purpose of the heat induction unit may have been similar to that of the [[rheostat]], and it may be possible that the two devices were one and the same.

